Given account and provider details:-

provider "aws" {
  access_key = "aaaaaaaaaaaaaa"
  secret_key = "aaaaaaaaaaaa"
  region     = "us-west-10"
}



Creating ec2 with tags

resource "aws_instance" "myinstance" {
  ami           = "ami-000000"
  instance_type = "t2.micro"
  tags = {
    Name = "mycode"
  }
}


codes :-
terraform init
terraform fmt
terraform plan
terraform apply 



